Sample Email Writing

Dear Sir/ Madam/ Hiring Manager,

I am writing to express my strong interest and willingness to apply for the position of “Sales Executive” in your organization.

I believe that my education and experience make me a highly competitive candidate for this position. Furthermore, I hope that working as a Sales Executive in your esteemed organization will give me the opportunity to enhance my skills and contribute to your company.  I am enthusiastic about the opportunity to contribute my skills and experience to your team. I have a proven track record of (mention one or two key accomplishments or skills relevant to the job), and I am confident in my ability to (mention how you can benefit the company).

Here, I would like to mention that I have acquired the necessary skills over the past couple of years in sales and marketing.

Please find my resume attached herewith.

Thank you for considering my application.  Please feel free to contact me at (Your Phone Number) or via email at (Your Email Address) to schedule an interview.

Sincerely,
(Your Full Name)



